text: Le Poiré-sur-Velluire is a former commune. It is found in the region Pays de la Loire in the Vendée department in the west of France. On 1 January 2019, it became a part of the new commune of Les Velluire-sur-Vendée.Arrêté préfectoral 17 August 2018 == References == Category:Former communes in Vendée
title: Le Poiré-sur-Velluire
